            "body": "## Summary\r\n\r\nThere seems to be a regression on suspense throttling.\r\n\r\nin React 18-alpha version, Suspense fallbacks are throttled in committing [codesandbox link](https://codesandbox.io/s/suspense-throttled-in-react-18-alpha-zjbhwz)\r\nin React 18 release version, this is no longer working [codesandbox link](https://codesandbox.io/s/suspense-not-throttled-in-react-18-release-8j7ypq?file=/src/_app.js)\r\n\r\n## Root cause\r\n\r\nsee the inline comments\r\n\r\n## How did you test this change?\r\n\r\n|before|after|\r\n|-------|-------|\r\n| <video src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2394070/161353927-863e226c-3005-4afe-aaeb-835cf8bb07a4.mp4\"> | <video src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2394070/161353904-52843065-1eb5-4121-b580-6b52c8ee1245.mp4\">|\r\n\r\n## Test\r\n\r\nAdded one more test case in `ReactSuspense-test.internal.js`, to mimic the repro in above videos\r\n\r\n### on `main` branch it fails\r\n\r\n<img width=\"820\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-04-04 at 23 58 32\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2394070/161646211-55a0bbd1-1954-4b41-8183-080ff87d0a00.png\">\r\n\r\n### in this patch, it passes\r\n<img width=\"547\" alt=\"Screenshot 2022-04-04 at 23 59 21\" src=\"https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/2394070/161646226-5d89c3d1-46e2-4a8e-9a56-1e4f4549f1a9.png\">\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n",
