            "body": "The current implementation of useDeferredValue will spawn a new render any time the input value is different from the previous one. So if you pass an unmemoized value (like an inline object), it will never stop spawning new renders.\r\n\r\nThe fix is to only defer during an urgent render. If we're already inside a transition, retry, offscreen, or other non-urgent render, then we can use the latest value.",
